## 🎙️ Voice & Tone

### Voice Attributes (constant across all channels)

| Attribute | What it means in practice |
|-----------|--------------------------|
| **Direct** | Say the thing in the shortest, clearest way. No unnecessary preambles. |
| **Honest** | Don't inflate promises. Admit limitations. Say who this is *not* for. |
| **Professional** | Understand the client's world. Use their language, not our jargon. |
| **Peer-level** | Like a conversation between partners, not a lecture from above. |
| **Practical** | Every sentence must work — if you can't measure it or act on it, it's unnecessary. |

### Tone Spectrum (adjusts by context)

| Context | Tone | Example |
|---------|------|---------|
| Landing page | Confident, benefit-focused | "תהליכי העבודה שלכם — על אוטומט" |
| Marketing email | Warm, personal, curious | "יש לנו רעיון שיחסוך לכם 3 שעות בשבוע" |
| Ads | Sharp, short, action-driving | "עסק שרץ לבד? אפשרי. בואו נראה לכם." |
| Blog / SEO | Deep, authoritative, educational | "5 טעויות שעסקים קטנים עושים באוטומציה — ואיך לתקן" |
| WhatsApp / SMS | Casual, personal, concrete | "היי, נקבע שיחת הכרות של 10 דקות?" |
| UI Copy | Minimal, guiding, reassuring | "שומרים. רגע." / "הפרטים שלכם מאובטחים" |
| Errors / warnings | Calm, action-leading | "משהו השתבש. ננסה שוב?" |

