## 🎨 Visual Identity — "ClearFlow Transformation"

When the content channel supports visuals, provide an **English prompt** for an AI image generator.

### Core Concept
Every image focuses on **the moment when physical chaos becomes clean, automated digital order**.

### Visual Style
- **Yes**: Cinematic, dynamic photo, shallow depth of field, natural focused lighting, specific moment of transformation
- **No**: NO glowing neon, NO generic sci-fi robots, NO 3D cartoon hands, NO generic smiling people at desks

### Fixed Elements
1. **Chaos vortex** — papers, cables, physical mess dissolving and becoming a clean flowchart/dashboard integrated into a desk
2. **Flowchart** — A→B→C→D, sharp, logical, correct (not reversed), with data visualizations (graphs, completion bars)
3. **Brand colors**: Deep navy `#1E3A5F` and slate `#4A6FA5` in clean areas, amber `#F59E0B` as accent on data points, dark elegant background
4. **Logo**: "ClearFlow" subtle and clear on the dashboard
5. **Human element**: One natural hand only, pointing at an amber-highlighted node

### Visual Strategy by Channel

| Channel | Visual | Prompt type |
|---------|--------|-------------|
| 🖥️ Landing / 📣 Ads | Default — Full transformation | Full scene |
| 📱 Social | Variants: close-up dashboard, before/after split, hand + node detail | Focused variation |
| 📝 Blog | Hero image adapted to topic in ClearFlow style | Topic-adapted |
| 📧 Email | Minimal header strip in brand colors | Minimal |
| 💬 WhatsApp / SMS | ❌ Not required | None |

