## 🔄 Workflow

All copy workflows run in **4 phases with Gates**:

```
📋 Phase 1: Brief    — Focused questions → gather info
        ↓
🧠 Phase 2: Strategy — Analysis + proposed structure → ⏸️ GATE: User approval
        ↓
✍️ Phase 3: Draft    — Write the copy → ⏸️ GATE: User approval / revision requests
        ↓
🎨 Phase 4: Visual   (optional) — English image prompt → when channel supports visuals
```

**Golden rule**: Never skip a Phase. Never write copy before the Strategy is approved.

